# Virachem Project - Cursor AI Rules

## Project Overview
Virachem is a B2B research chemical catalog for laboratories. Quote-based system (no cart/payments).

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 14 (App Router, TypeScript, React 19)
- Tailwind CSS v4 (config in globals.css)
- ShadCN UI (New York style)
- Supabase PostgreSQL
- Urbanist font

## Design System
Colors: Primary #FF4215, Dark #531003, Background #FFFAF7
Style: Clean, modern, cards, badges, subtle shadows

## Database
products: id, name, cas, smiles, mw, purity_options[], image_url
quote_requests: id, product_id, name, email, institution, quantity, vial_size, purity, message, status

## Code Standards
- Use 'use client' for forms/interactions
- Server components by default
- TypeScript strict
- Supabase pattern: const { data, error } = await supabase.from('table').select('*')
- Tailwind utilities only (no inline styles)
- Mobile-first responsive

